Yup.  For the interested, I took the first paragraph of Herbert
O. Yardley's "The American Black Chamber" as my plaintext, and
the next-to-last paragraph (picked more-or-less at random) on
page 587 of David Kahn's "The Codebreakers" as my key.

>There's one typo in the cryptogram... I'll leave it to the devoted reader
